# clasp push (from this dir) targets the standalone admin/service Apps Script
# project that hosts the promo redemption Web App. Allowlist only the three
# .gs files that belong in that project plus the manifest. FoundingMemberMonitor.gs
# is intentionally excluded — it is unrelated dev tooling for a different
# personal monitoring script.
**/**
!appsscript.json
!PromoCodeAdmin.gs
!PromoCodeService.gs
!PromoCodeServiceTests.gs
